Package: dolphin-emu-libretro
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dolphin-emu-data-libretro (= ${source:Version})
Conflicts: dolphin-emu, dolphin-emu-trunk
Replaces: dolphin-emu, dolphin-emu-trunk
Description: GameCube and Wii emulator
 Dolphin is a GameCube and Wii emulator.
 .
 Game compatibility is very good: a lot of GameCube and Wii titles work, but
 the emulator might require a lot of processing power in order to run some
 games at full speed.
 .
 GameCube and Wii are registered trademarks of Nintendo of America Inc. Dolphin
 is not affiliated with or endorsed by the company mentioned.

