Package: dolphin-emu-data-libretro
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Replaces: dolphin-emu-libretro (<< 5.0+git-r201701262047)
Breaks: dolphin-emu-libretro (<< 5.0+git-r201701262047)
Conflicts: dolphin-emu-data
Suggests: dolphin-emu-libretro
Description: Gamecube and Wii emulator - data files
 Dolphin is a GameCube, Wii and Triforce (the arcade machine based on the
 GameCube) emulator.
 .
 Game compatibility is very good: a lot of GameCube and Wii titles work, but
 the emulator might require a lot of processing power in order to run some
 games at full speed.
 .
 GameCube and Wii are registered trademarks of Nintendo of America Inc. Dolphin
 is not affiliated with or endorsed by the company mentioned.
 .
 This package provides the platform independent data files for Dolphin.
